value: Breeds (chiefly east of the 100th meridian) in southern Canada and the United States from southern Manitoba, northern Michigan, southern Ontario, southern Quebec, New Brunswick and Nova Scotia south to southern Louisiana and northern Florida. Winters from southern Mis- souri, the Ohio Valley and southern New Jersey to the Gulf coast and central Florida.
